---
// About Us Section Component
---

<section id="about" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            Tentang Fabrik Safety
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4" style="line-height: 1.3em;">
            Mitra Terpercaya Perlengkapan Safety Sejak 2018
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Fabrik Safety hadir sebagai solusi lengkap untuk kebutuhan pakaian safety dan perlengkapan kerja di Indonesia. Kami memproduksi wearpack, coverall, dan berbagai perlengkapan safety berkualitas tinggi dengan harga kompetitif.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Quality Terjamin</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Setiap produk melewati quality control ketat untuk memastikan standar kualitas terbaik.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Pengiriman Cepat</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Produksi sendiri memungkinkan kami menyelesaikan order dengan waktu yang lebih cepat.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Harga Kompetitif</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Harga langsung dari produsen tanpa perantara, cocok untuk kebutuhan corporate.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <a href="https://wa.me/62851111204599" class="btn-primary">
            Hubungi Kami
            <svg class="inline-block w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Images -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504307651254-35680f356dfd?w=400&h=500&fit=crop"
                alt="Production facility"
                class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=400&h=300&fit=crop"
                alt="Safety equipment"
                class="w-full h-36 object-cover"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 pt-8">
            <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=400&h=300&fit=crop"
                alt="Safety equipment"
                class="w-full h-36 object-cover"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504307651254-35680f356dfd?w=400&h=500&fit=crop"
                alt="Workers wearing safety equipment"
                class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
